Farmer and the Deli has been such a gift to Chesterland.  In a town with the worst Giant Eagle ever!  Farmer and the Deli is a great alternative to get fresh produce.  Farmer and the Deli has a variety of produce, meats, cheese, prepared food and more.  They carry Boars head meats.  Farmer and the Deli makes their own bread and have different prepared food everyday.  They have great subs!  There is house roast beef with Havarti jalapeno cheese is to die for!  Farmers staff is great- always greeting you with a smile.  It is always a pleasure to go to Farmer and the Deli